  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dbb \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dd2 \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0dc4\u0dd0\u0db1\u0d9a \u0db4\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0d87\u0dad\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dc4 \u0dc0\u0db1 \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dcf \u0da2\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dad\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dba\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An elephant and two wild elephants died after getting tangled in an unauthorized power line",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Anuradhapura Wildlife Office says that an elephant and two wild elephants were found dead yesterday (14th) after they got tangled in an unauthorized power line.",
        "This elephant and the two wild elephants have died due to electric shock after getting entangled in an unauthorized electric cable which had been pulled by a person in Ulagama Pudukkulama area of \u200b\u200bMihintale, wildlife department officials said.",
        "Locals say that a large herd of elephants hit this village on the night of Perera (13th) and at that time this elephant and the two elephants may have lost their lives by hitting the electric wires.",
        "In the morning, a person who went to visit the cattle was seen in the area and steps were taken to inform the officials of the wildlife department.",
        "The wildlife division also said that an investigation has been started to arrest the owner of the land who had laid the unauthorized electric wires in connection with this incident."
      ],
